1
00:00:18,973 --> 00:00:21,133
I'm finally gonna meet him.

2
00:00:25,193 --> 00:00:26,074
Excuse me.

3
00:00:27,293 --> 00:00:28,953
What a rude guy.

4
00:00:29,374 --> 00:00:30,013
Are you okay?

5
00:00:30,013 --> 00:00:30,673
I'm fine.

6
00:00:45,494 --> 00:00:48,093
Are you okay?

7
00:00:49,494 --> 00:00:50,733
I'm fine.

8
00:00:50,833 --> 00:00:51,534
That's good.

9
00:00:51,873 --> 00:00:52,954
I'm in a hurry. I gotta go.

10
00:00:53,814 --> 00:00:54,134
Bye.

11
00:01:07,473 --> 00:01:08,233
Watch out.

12
00:01:08,513 --> 00:01:09,273
Watch out.

13
00:01:13,514 --> 00:01:14,433
Sorry, buddy.

14
00:01:16,493 --> 00:01:18,213
Watch out. What are you doing?

15
00:01:18,553 --> 00:01:20,833
Sorry, I'm late.

16
00:01:20,973 --> 00:01:22,734
You are the one...

17
00:01:24,594 --> 00:01:25,114
Yes.

18
00:01:26,553 --> 00:01:29,314
You've been contacting me.

19
00:01:34,174 --> 00:01:34,433
Hello.

20
00:01:35,374 --> 00:01:36,154
My name is Wu Xi.

21
00:01:38,174 --> 00:01:39,254
My name is Ye Zhimei.

22
00:02:10,394 --> 00:02:11,254
Mr. Ye, Mr. Wu.

23
00:02:11,254 --> 00:02:12,014
Long time no see.

24
00:02:13,254 --> 00:02:14,394
The two people you'll meet later

25
00:02:14,573 --> 00:02:15,954
will be of great help to you.

26
00:02:16,454 --> 00:02:17,213
Mr. Wu.

27
00:02:19,974 --> 00:02:20,734
Zhimei,

28
00:02:21,234 --> 00:02:22,574
this is Uncle Wang,

29
00:02:22,873 --> 00:02:23,514
and this is Uncle Li.

30
00:02:24,114 --> 00:02:25,493
They are both old friends of my father.

31
00:02:26,114 --> 00:02:28,653
They might be able to help with the company's funding issue.

32
00:02:29,653 --> 00:02:31,493
So you must be Young Master Ye.

33
00:02:32,414 --> 00:02:34,914
We've heard about the situation in Chenghai.

34
00:02:34,974 --> 00:02:36,713
It's not easy for young people

35
00:02:37,273 --> 00:02:37,914
to take on everything.

36
00:02:38,634 --> 00:02:39,354
It's not easy.

37
00:02:40,833 --> 00:02:42,713
The company is going through a tough time,

38
00:02:43,114 --> 00:02:44,914
and we need your help.

39
00:02:47,514 --> 00:02:48,313
Mr. Wu,

40
00:02:48,313 --> 00:02:49,394
everything's arranged as you asked.

41
00:02:49,394 --> 00:02:50,574
Okay, I see.

42
00:02:52,114 --> 00:02:53,234
What did you arrange?

43
00:02:54,174 --> 00:02:55,014
A little surprise.

44
00:02:55,394 --> 00:02:56,653
You'll see in a bit.

45
00:02:58,253 --> 00:02:58,674
Excuse me,

46
00:02:59,114 --> 00:02:59,794
I'll be right back.

47
00:03:00,114 --> 00:03:00,974
Okay.

48
00:03:01,114 --> 00:03:01,674
Okay.

49
00:03:03,313 --> 00:03:04,074
I never thought

50
00:03:04,273 --> 00:03:06,153
the Wu family would fall this far.

51
00:03:06,753 --> 00:03:07,273
This guy

52
00:03:07,954 --> 00:03:09,234
managed to hook up

53
00:03:09,234 --> 00:03:11,114
with a rich lady like Miss Ye.

54
00:03:11,433 --> 00:03:13,114
Back then, he was so picky,

55
00:03:13,313 --> 00:03:14,674
it was hard for us to even meet.

56
00:03:15,114 --> 00:03:17,813
Now he's learned to leverage,

57
00:03:18,234 --> 00:03:19,773
that's some progress.

58
00:03:27,433 --> 00:03:30,794
I recently raised a billion dollars in funds,

59
00:03:31,273 --> 00:03:33,053
and I'm looking for good projects.

60
00:03:33,114 --> 00:03:34,433
A billion?

61
00:03:39,933 --> 00:03:40,354
Chairman Li,

62
00:03:40,553 --> 00:03:41,833
if I remember correctly,

63
00:03:42,553 --> 00:03:43,514
your company is under investigation

64
00:03:43,514 --> 00:03:44,493
by the CSRC,

65
00:03:45,114 --> 00:03:46,514
and your overseas accounts have been frozen.

66
00:03:47,234 --> 00:03:48,653
At such a critical time,

67
00:03:48,653 --> 00:03:50,433
you can still offer a billion dollars.

68
00:03:51,253 --> 00:03:52,234
That's really impressive.

69
00:03:52,234 --> 00:03:54,313
This is Mr. Zhou from Lanze Capital.

70
00:03:55,333 --> 00:03:56,974
Why are you here?

71
00:03:57,333 --> 00:03:57,933
You're here too?

72
00:03:58,414 --> 00:03:58,993
Alright, alright.

73
00:03:59,194 --> 00:04:00,433
Let's go.

74
00:04:04,894 --> 00:04:05,734
Is this the solution

75
00:04:05,734 --> 00:04:06,914
your ex-husband found for you?

76
00:04:08,593 --> 00:04:09,653
This is my business in Chenghai.

77
00:04:10,734 --> 00:04:11,313
Mr. Zhou,

78
00:04:11,313 --> 00:04:13,134
aren't you being too nosy?

79
00:04:13,474 --> 00:04:14,854
Why keep avoiding me?

80
00:04:15,894 --> 00:04:17,093
Because I don't like

81
00:04:17,414 --> 00:04:18,414
the conditions you set.

82
00:04:38,013 --> 00:04:38,993
Zhi Mei,

83
00:04:40,614 --> 00:04:41,373
I'm sorry.

84
00:04:43,053 --> 00:04:43,654
Let go of me.

85
00:04:43,813 --> 00:04:44,573
Zhi Mei,

86
00:04:45,114 --> 00:04:46,594
after all those days together,

87
00:04:47,154 --> 00:04:48,693
didn't you fall for me even a little?

88
00:04:49,013 --> 00:04:49,953
From the start,

89
00:04:50,534 --> 00:04:52,154
it was a carefully planned deception.

90
00:04:52,493 --> 00:04:53,433
What do you want me to fall for?

91
00:05:04,873 --> 00:05:06,573
But your heart doesn't lie.

92
00:05:09,414 --> 00:05:10,294
It never did,

93
00:05:11,253 --> 00:05:13,753
and it never will.

94
00:05:46,294 --> 00:05:47,693
Do you hate me that much?

95
00:05:52,654 --> 00:05:53,534
Zhi Mei,

96
00:05:55,594 --> 00:05:56,594
my decision

97
00:05:57,013 --> 00:05:57,993
was just to let you know

98
00:05:58,693 --> 00:06:00,334
how much I care about you.

99
00:06:12,834 --> 00:06:13,914
I'm sorry

100
00:06:15,114 --> 00:06:16,654
that I wasn't there for you

101
00:06:16,914 --> 00:06:17,953
when you needed me the most.

102
00:06:18,614 --> 00:06:20,334
But fate has given me another chance

103
00:06:20,714 --> 00:06:22,534
to come back to you.

104
00:06:22,794 --> 00:06:23,474
So,

105
00:06:24,313 --> 00:06:24,953
will you

106
00:06:24,953 --> 00:06:25,974
give me another chance

107
00:06:26,714 --> 00:06:28,393
to be with you?

108
00:06:29,013 --> 00:06:30,214
Yes!

109
00:06:30,214 --> 00:06:39,234
Say yes!

110
00:06:39,674 --> 00:06:40,493
Say yes!

111
00:06:46,433 --> 00:06:47,414
Say yes!

112
00:06:57,414 --> 00:06:58,834
What a touching scene!

113
00:07:00,013 --> 00:07:00,693
But

114
00:07:01,534 --> 00:07:03,114
if you love each other,

115
00:07:03,794 --> 00:07:05,873
why force her

116
00:07:06,373 --> 00:07:07,354
to make a public statement?

117
00:07:08,234 --> 00:07:08,714
Zhiwei,

118
00:07:09,114 --> 00:07:09,693
don't listen to him.

119
00:07:10,114 --> 00:07:11,854
I've always been sincere

120
00:07:12,114 --> 00:07:12,974
to you.

121
00:07:13,654 --> 00:07:15,174
You just took advantage of the situation,

122
00:07:15,594 --> 00:07:16,553
using your acting

123
00:07:16,553 --> 00:07:17,873
to cover up your own unease.

124
00:07:18,433 --> 00:07:19,654
You don't even know

125
00:07:20,114 --> 00:07:20,693
what Zhimei needs most.

126
00:07:20,834 --> 00:07:21,253
Yes,

127
00:07:21,873 --> 00:07:22,594
I am uneasy.

128
00:07:23,573 --> 00:07:24,953
I saw her

129
00:07:25,974 --> 00:07:27,674
get hurt deeply

130
00:07:27,813 --> 00:07:28,974
by your so-called deep affection.

131
00:07:29,114 --> 00:07:29,774
And you,

132
00:07:30,193 --> 00:07:32,053
a person full of lies,

133
00:07:32,114 --> 00:07:33,253
to judge me.

134
00:07:35,493 --> 00:07:36,253
Zhimei.

135
00:07:49,334 --> 00:07:49,734
You...

136
00:07:49,734 --> 00:07:50,234
Enough.

137
00:07:51,534 --> 00:07:52,274
I don't need you

138
00:07:52,834 --> 00:07:54,094
to make decisions for me.

139
00:07:56,674 --> 00:07:56,953
Zhimei.

140
00:07:57,094 --> 00:07:57,433
Zhimei.

141
00:08:12,714 --> 00:08:14,474
Brother, it's you.

142
00:08:20,174 --> 00:08:21,053
You look worn out.

143
00:08:23,654 --> 00:08:25,914
A lot has happened recently.

144
00:08:27,193 --> 00:08:30,073
Now I just want to keep Chenghai.

145
00:08:32,873 --> 00:08:35,174
Don't worry. I'm here for you.

146
00:08:36,813 --> 00:08:37,573
I will

147
00:08:37,573 --> 00:08:39,274
help you get through this.

148
00:08:42,934 --> 00:08:43,413
Yeah.

149
00:08:44,373 --> 00:08:45,373
All these years,

150
00:08:45,793 --> 00:08:46,993
having you by my side,

151
00:08:47,114 --> 00:08:48,314
taking care of me,

152
00:08:48,533 --> 00:08:49,694
being my brother,

153
00:08:51,393 --> 00:08:51,913
it's really good.

154
00:08:53,814 --> 00:08:54,354
Yeah.

155
00:08:55,114 --> 00:08:56,074
That's what a brother does.

156
00:08:57,614 --> 00:08:58,133
Back then,

157
00:08:58,314 --> 00:08:59,373
my dad had the accident,

158
00:08:59,873 --> 00:09:01,114
if it weren't for your parents

159
00:09:01,114 --> 00:09:01,913
taking me in,

160
00:09:02,114 --> 00:09:03,094
paying for my education,

161
00:09:03,834 --> 00:09:04,554
and raising me,

162
00:09:06,454 --> 00:09:07,173
I really don't know

163
00:09:07,293 --> 00:09:08,913
what I would be like today.

164
00:09:08,913 --> 00:09:09,554
I will remember this kindness

165
00:09:10,474 --> 00:09:11,554
for the rest of my life.

166
00:09:12,673 --> 00:09:13,454
So Xiaomei,

167
00:09:14,234 --> 00:09:14,993
no matter what,

168
00:09:16,434 --> 00:09:17,114
I will help you.

169
00:09:29,074 --> 00:09:31,253
You've put on a touching play,

170
00:09:31,314 --> 00:09:33,214
but your heroine doesn't like it.

171
00:09:34,194 --> 00:09:35,734
It's between me and Zhimei.

172
00:09:36,114 --> 00:09:37,273
You, an outsider,

173
00:09:37,273 --> 00:09:38,773
have no right to interfere.

174
00:09:40,493 --> 00:09:41,253
Outsider?

175
00:09:42,354 --> 00:09:43,273
Do you know

176
00:09:43,793 --> 00:09:45,694
Zhimei doesn't like spicy food anymore?

177
00:09:46,114 --> 00:09:46,594
Do you know

178
00:09:47,114 --> 00:09:48,373
she prefers rainy days

179
00:09:48,934 --> 00:09:50,334
to sunny days?

180
00:09:50,633 --> 00:09:52,334
Do you know when she lies,

181
00:09:52,694 --> 00:09:54,893
when she lies?

182
00:09:58,373 --> 00:10:00,094
It seems that you don't know her well.

183
00:10:03,854 --> 00:10:04,454
Do you know

184
00:10:05,114 --> 00:10:06,393
her ears will turn red

185
00:10:07,273 --> 00:10:09,074
when she is in love?

186
00:10:14,094 --> 00:10:14,834
I owe her

187
00:10:15,114 --> 00:10:16,354
for this punch.

188
00:10:16,354 --> 00:10:17,513
But I don't owe you.

189
00:10:18,293 --> 00:10:19,574
You failed to protect her.

190
00:10:19,694 --> 00:10:20,993
You've lost your chance.

191
00:10:21,114 --> 00:10:21,954
This time,

192
00:10:22,234 --> 00:10:23,493
I won't give in.

193
00:10:35,493 --> 00:10:36,153
Wu Xi.

194
00:10:42,354 --> 00:10:42,913
Wu Xi.

195
00:10:44,653 --> 00:10:45,513
Are you okay?

196
00:10:46,094 --> 00:10:46,854
I'm fine.

197
00:10:48,893 --> 00:10:49,454
Zhimei.
